- **`internal/tui/model.go`** — `myView bool` → `viewMode ViewMode`, `New()` now accepts `StateStore` and loads state at construction; `saveState()` uses the store interface
- **`internal/tui/model_test.go`** — `noopStore{}` test double (same-package, no I/O)
- **`internal/tui/export_test.go`** — `MyView()` returns `m.viewMode == ViewMine`
- **`internal/cmd/mrboard/board.go`** — wires `statestore.YAMLStore` using `config.XDGDataDir()`

